FBIS3-8078 "dreeu043_i_94016" FBIS-EEU-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Serb Forces in Srebrenica Demilitarized Zone AU0303200994 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 1800 GMT 3 Mar 94 AU0303200994 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Text] The forces of the Serbian aggressor this afternoon took up positions in the area of Podravanje, which is situated within the demilitarized zone of Srebrenica.
